The server ignores any player updates that exceed 20000 or -20000 in X or Y axis and reports the last position that was within the bounds, making the streamer think you haven&#39;t moved. To increase the boundaries, you can use `SetSyncBounds` in [YSF][1]:

    const Float:FLOAT_INFINITY = Float:0x7F800000;
    SetSyncBounds(-FLOAT_INFINITY, FLOAT_INFINITY, -FLOAT_INFINITY, FLOAT_INFINITY);

This will accept any finite coordinates, which should be enough for any map.

  [1]: https://github.com/IllidanS4/YSF

